# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:10
translate portuguese micha13_66a911ed:

    # "When I get to the counselor's office, I'm surprised to see Gertrude behind the counter instead of Mi-Cha."
    "Quando chego ao gabinete da conselheira, fico surpreendido ao ver a Gertrude atrás do balcão em vez da Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:11
translate portuguese micha13_51f359cb:

    # sc "Good morning, [pcname]. If you're here for a counseling session, I'm sorry. I have to work reception today."
    sc "Bom dia, [pcname]. Se estás aqui para uma sessão de aconselhamento, desculpa. Hoje tenho de trabalhar na receção."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:12
translate portuguese micha13_320f7ecc:

    # pc "Where's Mi-Cha?"
    pc "Onde está a Mi-Cha?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:13
translate portuguese micha13_f822911c:

    # sc "She called this morning saying she couldn't come in for some reason. She sounded upset."
    sc "Ela ligou esta manhã a dizer que não podia vir por alguma razão. Parecia chateada."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:14
translate portuguese micha13_d6ed663d:

    # sc "If you have time, maybe you could go check on her? I know you two have become friends."
    sc "Se tiveres tempo, talvez pudesses ir ver como ela está? Sei que vocês os dois se tornaram amigos."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:15
translate portuguese micha13_477e82cd:

    # pc "Yeah, I think I have a little time before class. I'll go do that."
    pc "Sim, acho que tenho um pouco de tempo antes da aula. Vou fazer isso."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:18
translate portuguese micha13_cfda0a84:

    # "I leave the counselor's office, walk over to the dorms, and make my way up to Mi-Cha's door."
    "Saio do gabinete da conselheira, caminho até aos dormitórios e dirijo-me à porta da Mi-Cha."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:22
translate portuguese micha13_90464c94:

    # "She answers after a couple of knocks."
    "Ela atende após algumas batidas."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:23
translate portuguese micha13_94a711d9:

    # mc "Oh, [pcname]! Why are you here?"
    mc "Oh, [pcname]! Porque estás aqui?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:24
translate portuguese micha13_36eedc65:

    # pc "Gertrude asked me to come check on you. She said you called in. Are you sick?"
    pc "A Gertrude pediu-me para vir ver como estavas. Ela disse que ligaste. Estás doente?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:25
translate portuguese micha13_2e46b23a:

    # mc "No, I'm not sick."
    mc "Não, não estou doente."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:26
translate portuguese micha13_cb45e08c:

    # pc "Well, what's going on?"
    pc "Bem, o que se passa?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:29
translate portuguese micha13_98c909b0:

    # "I follow her inside and we sit on her bed."
    "Entro com ela e sentamo-nos na cama dela."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:30
translate portuguese micha13_2f43efba:

    # mc "I argued with my parents last night. They told me to quit dance class. They say that it interferes with my studies."
    mc "Discuti com os meus pais ontem à noite. Disseram-me para desistir das aulas de dança. Dizem que isso interfere nos meus estudos."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:31
translate portuguese micha13_6282a1b7:

    # pc "But you like dancing."
    pc "Mas tu gostas de dançar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:34
translate portuguese micha13_44899e27:

    # mc "I love dancing. And I have a performance soon that I was very much looking forward to."
    mc "Adoro dançar. E tenho uma apresentação em breve pela qual estava ansiosa."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:35
translate portuguese micha13_4624f9be:

    # mc "But they say that I have to stop."
    mc "Mas eles dizem que tenho de parar."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:36
translate portuguese micha13_ff3c6bab:

    # pc "So what?"
    pc "E então?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:37
translate portuguese micha13_f0ac6ad2:

    # mc "I can't just not do what they say."
    mc "Não posso simplesmente não fazer o que eles dizem."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:40
translate portuguese micha13_23d549c1:

    # pc "But I want you to dance."
    pc "Mas eu quero que dancem."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:41
translate portuguese micha13_81709362:

    # mc "You do?"
    mc "Queres?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:42
translate portuguese micha13_6dba6230:

    # pc "Yes."
    pc "Sim."

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:43
translate portuguese micha13_27a4c741:

    # mc "Are you telling me to?"
    mc "Estás a dizer-me para o fazer?"

# game/Scenes/Micha/micha13.rpy:44
translate portuguese micha13_f43da382:

    # pc "Yes, Mi-Cha. I'm telling you to dance."
    pc "Sim, Mi-Cha. Estou a dizer-te para dançares."

